    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "With arms reminiscent of a sea star or an octopus and the bodies of lemurs, sea crawlers range all over Azlant\u2019s coasts. Sea crawlers sometimes eat fruit, but most prefer meat, lying in shallow waters and ambushing prey. A sea crawler is 5 feet long and weighs 70 pounds."
        }
    ],
